description: The conservation centre says it has seen an 80% fall in income since it closed on 24 March.
title: Coronavirus: Jersey Zoo faces 'uncertain future'
title_page: Coronavirus: Jersey Zoo faces 'uncertain future' - BBC News
maintext: Dr Dickie said: "Jersey Zoo is very much woven into the island's DNA and has been integral to the community for over 60 years but we urgently need help to ensure that our zoo will still be part of Jersey's future."
